event.title: EVENT SHOPPING
event.descriptions: Do you have an event fast approaching? A personal stylist can take all of the stress out of shopping for that special outfit. We will meet your personal style, shopping budget and occasion requirements. The shop will include clothing, shoe choice, and accessories. After the shop you will be sent the exact styling instructions that were provided on the day so you will have a step-by-step guide to keep. Comprehensive prior personal shopping questionnaire Mood board created prior to personal shopping with outfits suggestions meeting your event dress-code requirements. 1.5 hours personal shopping at convenient Sydney locations you can choose from. (For virtual clients online shopping options will be provided.). 1-week post-shop personal styling advice. No question is too big or small. We want you to feel fabulous at your event! Total Cost for Event Personal Styling and Personal Shopping $239.  Contact us for your expert styling experience!
